description:
The Fantastic Philadelphians - Volume 1 (1972 quad mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 AC3 @ 440kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.
Slight noise/crackle filtering applied (Izotope RX 2), no EQ, compression, or rear channel boost.

Converted from quad CD-4 vinyl using an AUDIO TECHNICA AT20SLa CD-4 cartridge / JVC 4DD-5 demodulator.


The Philadelphia Orchestra - Eugene Ormandy, Conductor

Chabrier - Espana
Dukas - The Sorcerer's Apprentice
